        | 'HANDLE_REDIRECT_COMPLETE';

        isLoading: true,

    case 'LOGIN_POPUP_COMPLETE':
    case 'INITIALISED':
      return {
        ...state,
        isAuthenticated: !!action.user,

        error: undefined,

    case 'GET_ACCESS_TOKEN_COMPLETE':

      }
      return {
        ...state,
        isAuthenticated: !!action.user,
        user: action.user,
      };
    case 'LOGOUT':
      return {
        ...state,
        isAuthenticated: false,
        user: undefined,
      };

      return {
        ...state,
        isLoading: false,
        error: action.error,
      };
  }

  );

    async (opts?: GetTokenSilentlyOptions): Promise<any> => {
      let token;
      try {
        token = await client.getTokenSilently(opts);
      } catch (error) {
        throw tokenError(error);
      } finally {
        dispatch({
          type: 'GET_ACCESS_TOKEN_COMPLETE',

      let token;

        token = await client.getTokenWithPopup(opts, config);

        dispatch({
          type: 'GET_ACCESS_TOKEN_COMPLETE',
          user: await client.getUser(),

      return token;
    },

  );

    (opts) => client.getIdTokenClaims(opts),

    async (url?: string): Promise<RedirectLoginResult> => {

    getAccessTokenSilently,
    getAccessTokenWithPopup,
    getIdTokenClaims,
    loginWithRedirect,
    loginWithPopup,
    logout,

  ]);
